oNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\"><em>You must be the change you wish to see in the</em> <em>world.</em></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nGaramond\">- </span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:Garamond\">Mahatma<strong> </strong>Gandhi<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;mso-outline-level:1\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">National Anthem</span></u></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;(1978-present)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Arise, O compatriots,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Nigeria\'s\r\ncall obey<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">To serve\r\nour fatherland<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">With love\r\nand strength and faith.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">The labour\r\nof our heroes past<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Shall\r\nnever be in vain,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">To serve\r\nwith heart and might<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">One nation\r\nbound in freedom, peace and unity.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">O God of creation<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Direct our\r\nnoble cause<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Guide our\r\nleader\'s right<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Help our\r\nyouth the truth to know<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">In love\r\nand honesty to grow<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">And living\r\njust and true<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Great\r\nlofty heights attain<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">To build a\r\nnation where peace<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2pt; margin-left: 36pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Garamond;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#252525;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">And\r\njustice shall reign.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nGaramond\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">The second stanza of the Nigerian\r\nanthem is a prayer, and the last line says, ...<strong><em>to build a nation where peace and\r\njustice shall reign</em>.</strong> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">&#8226;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Is\r\nthere peace in the country? With the Indigenous People of Biafra\'s (IPOB)\r\nagitations, kidnappings and killings by different terrorist organizations in\r\nNigeria, leadership instability, #resumeorresign etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">&#8226;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Is\r\nthere justice? Bribery and corruption being made the order of the day, criminals\r\ncelebrated, hidden loot found without the owners brought to book, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Going back to the first stanza of\r\nthe anthem, it says, <strong>...</strong> <strong><em>to\r\nserve our fatherland with love and strength and faith, ... to serve</em></strong><em> <strong>with\r\nheart and might</strong></em> <strong>... .</strong> How have\r\nyou served this nation? Have you served with love, strength and faith? Have we\r\ngiven our heart and might to our nation? If we cannot answer YES to the above\r\nquestions, then we are simply ARM CHAIR CRITICS. We keep complaining, yet do\r\nnothing to help the situation. We keep doing the same thing expecting a\r\ndifferent result. Women, we need to ARISE! Truth is we have no other country. Nigerians\r\nare very prayerful people; however, the focus of our prayer is only on personal\r\ndesires - \"Father, bless me with a life partner\", \"I need a job, promotion,\r\nchildren, divine health\", etc. Permit me to ask, \"Of what good are all these\r\nblessings in a country where there is no security of life and property?\" We\r\nspend very little time praying for our nation yet the Bible says in the PEACE\r\nof your nation lies your PEACE. Some people decide to \'check out\' of Nigeria\r\naltogether, hoping to escape the numerous issues that plague the nation, what\r\nthey forget is they will still have to come home from time to time to visit\r\ntheir loved ones and attend family events. Something really tragic happened\r\nsome years back, when a family of six came back just to attend a wedding in\r\nAbuja and on their way the plane crashed. May their beautiful souls rest in\r\nperfect peace. Nigeria needs you and I. Let us join hands together, we can\'t\r\nleave the rebuilding of this nation to others. Let us all do our part, the\r\nsolution is not absconding (except of course God has led you) the solution is\r\nin joining forces to fix the problem.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Let us BE THE CHANGE!</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/tenets/1505474628Picture1.png\" alt=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong style=\"font-family: Garamond; font-size: 12pt;\">Maslow\'s Hierarchy of Needs</strong><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Our desire for the basic needs of\r\nlife are normal but all the things we seek for (which may be good and necessary)\r\nare right down there at the bottom of the pyramid. This means psychology\r\nrecognizes their importance and so does God our creator, he just wants us to\r\nachieve those desires through another route. The Bible says, <strong>...<em>but\r\nseek ye first the kingdom of God, and His righteousness; and all these things\r\nshall be added unto you.<o:p></o:p></em></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nGaramond\">My Testimony</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">:&nbsp;\r\nThings seemed to always just work out for me until God decided to get my\r\nattention by not preventing the devil from sifting me; I had to wait eight\r\nyears for my second child. During the wait, the Lord said, \"Focus on Me\"; I\r\nthen started a fellowship called <em>Times of\r\nRefreshing</em>, organized hospital visits, etc. To the glory of God, I now have\r\nthe long awaited child and even more. He wants us to seek first His Kingdom and\r\nrighteousness and He surely will add all other things to us.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">The Lord calls us the salt of the\r\nearth and the light of the world. My sisters, the devil is gaining grounds and\r\nwe are losing grounds; why?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nGaramond;mso-fareast-font-family:Garamond;mso-bidi-font-family:Garamond\">(a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><!--[endif]--><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Compromise</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\"> - Are we\r\ncompromising? Give me that old time religion....LGBT now LGBTQ and the other new\r\n\'normal\' - what does the Bible say? We must love everyone as Christians because\r\nwe are all God\'s children but please don\'t let us rewrite the bible If God says\r\nan act is wrong, then it is as God does not change.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nGaramond;mso-fareast-font-family:Garamond;mso-bidi-font-family:Garamond\">(b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></strong><!--[endif]--><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">Hypocrisy and Pharisee-ism</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\"> - Some\r\npeople/churches \'sweat the small stuff\"; \"Don\'t wear make-up\", \"Don\'t wear\r\ntrousers\", etc. (please by all means, obey the doctrines of your church, I also\r\nobey mine). Let us, however, focus on the real thing - Christian LOVE! How do you\r\nshow God\'s love to the world? Do you radiate God\'s love? Do you care for people\r\naround you? Or are we just non make-up wearing, non trouser wearing nasty and\r\nunkind people? Faith in, and love for God must reflect in our LOVE for people.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Garamond\">It\'s time for ACTION, enough 