ns */\ntable.MsoNormalTable\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\";\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\n	mso-style-priority:99;\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-para-margin-top:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt;\n	mso-para-margin-left:0cm;\n	text-align:justify;\n	text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n	line-height:115%;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;}\ntable.MsoTableGrid\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Grid\";\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\n	mso-style-priority:59;\n	mso-style-unhide:no;\n	border:solid black 1.0pt;\n	mso-border-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\n	mso-border-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid black;\n	mso-border-insideh-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid black;\n	mso-border-insidev-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n	text-align:justify;\n	text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n\n\n<!--StartFragment-->\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;color:#282828\">There are days when we feel very productive\nand we tend to do a lot more than requested and achieve a lot more, in the end.\nOn other days, however, we find it difficult to work and even harder to\nconcentrate on our tasks and goals for the day. Just in case you find yourself\nin one of these conditions, be still and know we\'ve all been there and done\nthat before.<o:p></o:p></span></p><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;color:#282828\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;color:#282828\">Let the following quotes speak to you and help\nyou get past the day:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828\">1<strong>. <em>It doesn\'t matter how slowly you go, as long</em></strong><em> <strong>as\nyou don\'t stop</strong></em> --- <em>Confucius</em></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Arial;color:#282828\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828\">Oftentimes, we find out that we\'re moving at a slow\npace when we compare ourselves to our folks or people we feel we should be\ntogether with. Confucius, however, wants us to understand that we need to keep\nmoving and hope for better days.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828\">2. <strong><em><span style=\"background:#F9F9F9\">Promise me\nyou\'ll always remember: You\'re braver than you believe, and stronger than you\nseem, and smarter than you think</span></em></strong><em><span style=\"background:#F9F9F9\"> </span></em><span style=\"background:\n#F9F9F9\">--- <em>Christopher Robin</em><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">For days when you feel down and\nunable to go on and just entirely tired, remind yourself that you are brave,\nsmart, and strong.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">3. <strong><em>Tough times never last, but tough\npeople do</em></strong> --- <em>Robert H. Schuller</em><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">This may be hard to understand but\nvery real for people who get it. Tough times will come your way because, in the\nwords of Maya Angelou, you are human and nothing human is alien to you; but you\nneed to let go and be strong because those times never last.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">4. <strong><em>Don\'t be discouraged. It\'s often\nthe last key in the</em></strong><em> <strong>bunch that opens the lock</strong> ---</em> <em>Abraham Lincoln<o:p></o:p></em></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">For days when you feel you\'re not\ngood enough, or your efforts are underappreciated or mean little or nothing to\nthe growth of the organization, let Abraham Lincoln\'s words soothe your heart.<o:p></o:p></span></p><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">5. <strong><em>Challenges are what make life\ninteresting, and</em></strong><em> <strong>overcoming them is what makes life</strong> <strong>meaningful</strong> </em>--- <em>Joshua J. Marine<o:p></o:p></em></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">Does this speak volumes to you?\nBecause it clearly sums up everything. Always remember that your meaningful\nlife depends on you overcoming your challenges and killing your demons.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">6. <strong>Y<em>ou may encounter many defeats,\nbut you must not be defeated. In fact, it may be necessary to encounter the\ndefeats, so you can know who you are, what you can rise from, how you can still\ncome out of it</em></strong> --- <em>Maya Angelou<o:p></o:p></em></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">Maya Angelou says a lot of amazing\nstuff in her autobiography and of the many beautiful quotes, this is one that\nshould be a guiding principle for the everyday life. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">7. <strong><em>And once the storm is over, you\nwon\'t remember how you made it through, how you managed to survive. You won\'t\neven be sure whether the storm is really over. But one thing is certain --- when\nyou come out of the storm, you won\'t be the same person who walked in. That\'s\nwhat this storm\'s all about </em></strong>â€• <em>Haruki\nMurakami<o:p></o:p></em></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\">Haruki Murakami is the genius\nbehind the book called \'Norwegian Wood\' and this one sticks because asides it\'s\nsimilarity, it defines a reality as human beings. First, identifying that\nindeed the storm will end, and it will be a thing of the past and it will make\nyou an entirely different person.<o:p></o:p></span></p><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\nminor-bidi;color:#282828;background:#F9F9F9\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <w:WordDocument>\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\n  <w:Compatibility>\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\n 