yle Definitions */\ntable.MsoNormalTable\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\";\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\n	mso-style-priority:99;\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-para-margin-top:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt;\n	mso-para-margin-left:0cm;\n	text-align:justify;\n	text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n	line-height:115%;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;}\ntable.MsoTableGrid\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Grid\";\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\n	mso-style-priority:59;\n	mso-style-unhide:no;\n	border:solid black 1.0pt;\n	mso-border-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\n	mso-border-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid black;\n	mso-border-insideh-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid black;\n	mso-border-insidev-themecolor:text1;\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n	text-align:justify;\n	text-justify:inter-ideograph;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n\n\n<!--StartFragment-->\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\">Have you\never</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\">felt so lost\nbeing surrounded by noxious thoughts of shame and failure? Maybe you have even\nquestioned your existence without receiving any desirable</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\">response apart from the echoes of\nyour own guilt. Did your rigorous search for an escapade unfortunately end with\nrealities of insurmountable mountains that finally gave you up in resignation to\nhopelessness?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cheer up, you\nare not alone! <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>Many people have also traipsed\nthis daunting path with similar or</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\"> worse ordeal.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>A few of them, however, chose to end their\nstories remarkably, by counting one to gain much.</span><span style=\"font-size:\n14.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Without any doubt, you must have stumbled on the story of a young\nman who, long ago, found himself in a devastating circumstance, to which he\nlost everything including his family, friends and property. Instead of securing\nan enduring wealth by investing his billions, he misused this golden privilege and\ngambled his way into poverty. After a period, he became so impoverished that he\nlacked basic provision of food, clothing and shelter.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Life offered him only two alternatives: to continue to live\nwith pigs and share their fillings, or remember his identity and count on the goodness\nof his father. Suddenly, his brain jolted and he rationalized within himself, \"<em>How many of my father\'s hired servants have\nbread enough to eat and</em> <em>to spare, and\nI perish</em> <em>with hunger?\"</em> He\nconcluded that his father\'s goodwill was better than the anguish of poverty.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">That was the beginning of his breakthrough!</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Munching the fills of repugnant animals would never have resolved\nhis challenges. You can\'t root with hogs and have a clean nose (Mieder <em>et</em> <em>al</em>.\n1996 303).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">At no cost, ironically, but through free thinking, his life\nturned a new leaf, from shame to fame, focusing only on one good thing. By\ncounting on his father\'s good nature, his hope was restored and consequently,\nhe gained the following:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\">His father\'s\naffection<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\">His father\'s\nforgiveness<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\">A change in\nstatus (best robe, sandals and a ring)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\">A grand celebration\n(killing a fatted calf)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\">Affirmation\nby all <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%\">Reconciliation\nwith his family<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Can you remember any good thing you have enjoyed without having\nto pay for it -a good name, family, friends, growth in\neducation/business/career, intelligence, health, etc.? If you can focus on one\nof these God-given benefits, then you will experience the hope you require for your\ngreat change. Plug in on it and be amazed by the actualization of dreams. Gain\nhope and ride on the reality of your expectations. Hope does not make ashamed.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Many times, we are worried about the several requirements\nneeded to recover from all losses. A simple approach is to focus on only one\nthing at a time. <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>The Master of the\nuniverse, Jesus, confirmed this in His conversation with Martha, by redirecting\nher focus with these words, \"<em>But one\nthing is needed, and Mary has chosen that good part, which will not be taken\naway<strong> </strong>from<strong> </strong>her.\"<strong> </strong></em>Can we choose\nthis good part like Mary and just focus on one goodness? ONE IS ENOUGH.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Counting, a very elementary cognitive skill, has been\nrevealed by wisdom to be of significance in restoring our hope. Just like a\nsmall rudder on a huge ship is critical in setting its course in the face of\nthe strongest winds, counting is the required spark to set the forest of our\nhearts ablaze in hope.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Hope is the strength you need to rise from despondency to\nbliss. Receive hope today and enjoy a zenith transformation. It reassures you\nof the benefits you can receive freely, based on God\'s benevolence rather than\nyour own effort. At this point, it is never about you but God.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">You can return to the Father\'s love. Count one and gain much.\nDon\'t be left in misery. This is the real beauty in the Father\'s house.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Raleway;\">&nbsp;</span></p><!--EndFragment--><style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n@font-face\n	{font-family:Arial;\n	panose-1:2 11 6 4 2 2 2 2 2 4;\n	mso-font-charset:0;\n	mso-generic-font-family:auto;\n	mso-font-pitch:variable;\n	mso-font-signature:-536859905 -1073711037 9 0 511 0;}\n@font-face\n	{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n	panose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;\n	mso-font-charset:0;\n	mso-generic-font-family:auto;\n	mso-font-pitch:variable;\n	mso-font-signature:-536870145 1107305727 0 0 415 0;}\n@font-face\n	{font-family:Calibri;\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;\n	mso-font-charset:0;\n	mso-generic-font-family:auto;\n	mso-font-pitch:variable;\n	mso-font-signature:-536870145 1073786111 1 0 415 0;}\n /* Style Definitions */\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n	{mso-style-unhide:no;\n	mso-style-qformat:yes;\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\n	margin-top:0cm;\n	margin-right:0cm;\n	margin-bottom:10.0pt;\n	margin-left:0cm;\n	text-align:justify;\n	